'''WISEP J190648.47+401106.8'''（簡稱為'''W1906+40'''）是一顆[[棕矮星#光譜類型|L型矮星]]。在2015年，它被證實在表面上有類似[[木星|木星]][[大紅斑|大紅斑]]大小的風暴。 這個風暴大約每9小時繞行恆星一周，並且至少在2013年就已經觀測到這個風暴的存在<ref>{{cite web |title=NASA Telescopes Detect Jupiter-Like Storm on Small Star |url=http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?feature=4786 |work=[[Jet_Propulsion_Laboratory|Jet Propulsion Laboratory]] |date=10 December 2015 |accessdate=11 December 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108114347/http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?feature=4786 }}</ref>。

這顆恆星距離地球53光年，它的本質亮度只有太陽的0.0002（10<sup>−3.67±0.03</sup>L⊙），半徑是木星的0.9，表面溫度為2,038℃。這顆恆星有明顯的[[閃焰|閃焰]]（耀斑）發射<ref name="Simbad">{{cite web |title=WISEP J190648.47+401106.8 |url=http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=WISEP+J190648.47%2B401106.8 |work=SIMBAD |date=26 November 2015 |accessdate=11 December 2015 |archive-date=2021-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210831204028/https://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=WISEP+J190648.47%2B401106.8 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Mike |last=Wall |title=Dwarf Star Blasts out Stunningly Powerful Flares |url=http://www.space.com/21412-dwarf-star-flares-kepler-mission.html |work=[[Space.com|Space.com]] |date=3 June 2013 |accessdate=11 December 2015 |archive-date=2021-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509191814/https://www.space.com/21412-dwarf-star-flares-kepler-mission.html }}</ref><ref name="Gizis-et-al">{{cite arXiv |first=John E. |last=Gizis |display-authors=etal |title=Kepler Monitoring of an L Dwarf II. Clouds with Multiyear Lifetimes |arxiv=1509.07186|date=24 September 2015 }}</ref>。

